media/slideshow/13_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_sam_harris_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/13_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_sam_harris_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1706\" alt=\"Photography by Sam Harris.\" title=\"Photography by Sam Harris.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/13_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_sam_harris_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Sam Harris.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_sam_harris_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_sam_harris_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1792\" alt=\"Photography by Sam Harris.\" title=\"Photography by Sam Harris.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_sam_harris_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Sam Harris.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/34_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_rory_gardiner_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/34_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_rory_gardiner_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1600\" alt=\"Photography by Rory Gardiner.\" title=\"Photography by Rory Gardiner.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/34_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_rory_gardiner_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Rory Gardiner.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/25_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_rory_gardiner_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/25_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_rory_gardiner_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1600\" alt=\"Photography by Rory Gardiner.\" title=\"Photography by Rory Gardiner.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/25_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_rory_gardiner_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Rory Gardiner.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eGoodbye Horses’ romantic sensibility continues in the adjoining pour-over coffee shop Day Trip, featuring a small seated bar that offers views into the wine bar as well as access to a lush garden retreat. \u003cstrong\u003eDesigned in collaboration with Ji-Hae Hwang, an environmental artist and garden designer, the garden features a five-metre stone bench, quiet alcoves, and an oasis of verdant flora, creating a seamless indoor-outdoor transition. \u003c/strong\u003eReclaimed Yorkstone slabs and mature trees add layers of texture and tranquillity, further underscoring the project’s commitment to sustainability and natural beauty.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn a city as vibrant and ever-evolving as London, the two venues offer a refreshing antidote to the frenetic pace of urban life. The finished project provides a location where design, art, and gastronomy coalesce into an experience that is as thoughtful as it is transportive in what can only be described as a love letter to craftsmanship, community, and the enduring power of good design.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/17_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_adam_kang_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/17_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_adam_kang_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" alt=\"Photography by Adam Kang.\" title=\"Photography by Adam Kang.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/17_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_adam_kang_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Adam Kang.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/19_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_adam_kang_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/19_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_adam_kang_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1706\" alt=\"Douglas Conde (Head Barista). Photography by Adam Kang.\" title=\"Douglas Conde (Head Barista). Photography by Adam Kang.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/19_goodbye_horses_day_trip_dreamery_adam_kang_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDouglas Conde\u003c/s